thread.title: Jessie Newell

author: Jessie Newell
title: Jessie Newell
text: I work full time and go to school part time so figuring out everything that needed to be done and getting done was a huge hassle! Rushmypassport.com spells everything that you need out for you clearly with a checklist and different steps, and if you ever have any questions or concerns you can talk to someone to make sure that everything gets done correctly and avoid it bein sent back/rejected. Even after I received it, Merciline Ofelin followed up to make sure I'd received all my documents again. Thanks!
